    {
      "id": "detailed_3_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "This vehicle is in fair condition and remains a functional option for daily transportation. The exterior shows its age with several noticeable paint chips, scratches, and a few small dings. Inside, the cabin shows clear signs of use, including some staining on the carpets and wear on the seat bolsters. While the car starts and drives, it will likely need some mechanical attention in the near future, such as new tires or a brake service, to bring it back to peak performance.",
      "price": 18500.0,
      "reputation": 1.0,
